{"id": "art-31", "label": "Art. 31", "title": "Art. 31", "slug": "art-31", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 31 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_554572120\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2480\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_554572120\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Fondatorii <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> primii membri ai consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv ai directoratului <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ai consiliului de\nsupraveghere, sunt solidar r&#259;spunz&#259;tori, din momentul constituirii <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde societate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;i</span>\npentru:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1453618048\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2479\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1453618048\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- subscrierea integral&#259; a capitalului social <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> efectuarea v&#259;rs&#259;mintelor stabilite de <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i> sau de actul constitutiv;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_403960897\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2478\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_403960897\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- <span class=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span> aporturilor în\nnatur&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1281273725\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2477\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1281273725\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- veridicitatea <span class=SpellE>publica&#355;iilor</span>\nf&#259;cute în vederea constituirii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Fondatorii sunt\nr&#259;spunz&#259;tori, de asemenea, de valabilitatea <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunilor</span>\nîncheiate în contul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> înainte de\nconstituire <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> luate de aceasta asupra sa.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1200789743\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2476\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1200789743\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Adunarea general&#259; nu va putea da desc&#259;rcare\nfondatorilor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> primilor membri ai consiliului\nde <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv ai directoratului <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ai consiliului de supraveghere, pentru\nr&#259;spunderea ce le revine în temeiul prezentului articol <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> al art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>49</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>53</span><span style='color:black'>, timp de 5 ani.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}